					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-730289#post-1899633</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-730289/a-shift-at-the-factory#post-1899633</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2013 02:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Voct</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>392303</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;DO NOT INTIMIDATE THE WORKING MAN&quot;</p> <p>&quot;Robot&quot; is from the Czech for &quot;slave&quot; &#8212; or &quot;someone who is forced to labor for a master&quot;. It's cognate with &quot;arbeit&quot;, as in &quot;Arbeit Macht Frei&quot; (&quot;work shall make you free&quot;), the motto on the gates of Auschwitz.</p> <p>and a dude is a guy is a man.</p> <p>&quot;DO NOT INTIMIDATE THE WORKING MAN&quot;, a heroic message of defiance towards the evil bosses, becomes &quot;DO NOT INTIMIDATE ROBO-DUDE&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
